reviewText: The movie is OK,  if you speak German!!!! Luckily I  do some. Would be better if it was in english, but now I  own a dubed movie. The music was reported to be done by Eloy, this is not the case.

I thought that this was a sequel to the highly entreating mercenary movie "The Wild Geese". I suppose in some way, including the title, that it was. If I remed correctly, the plot was about breaking Albert Speer out of Spandau prison. I think that the only good thing about this one was mimsy Farmer
